/* note.g.json */.zh-CN: ❗重要配置❗，由github.com/chen56/note生成，一个笔记一个目录，每个目录都生成一个note.g.json，用来记录这篇笔记的重要元数据，比如生成note的uri, 文件应被保存在版本控制中，比如git，不应编辑或移动此文件。
/* note.g.json */.en: ❗ Important configuration ❗, generated by the github.com/chen56/note, one directory for each one note, note.g.json to record the important metadata of the note, for example generate the uri of note , the file should be saved in version control, such as git, and this file should not be edited or moved.
